  "short_description": "Ghoul Smash is a turn based physics game where you smash into enemies, fight bosses, and loot randomly generated items. With simplistic click-and-drag controls you can experience the thrill of smashing enemies into dust while gaining dopamine fueled rewards and progressing your character!",
