  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435910/extras/c27cb8932069f3c01a62b5ca12e194fb.poster.avif?t=1727827290\" width=618 height=78 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435910/extras/c27cb8932069f3c01a62b5ca12e194fb.webm?t=1727827290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435910/extras/c27cb8932069f3c01a62b5ca12e194fb.mp4?t=1727827290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Imagine if pool was transformed into an ARPG - that's Ghoul Smash! This turn-based physics game invites you to smash into enemies, face off against formidable bosses, and claim epic loot, craft gear, and invest into classes. With its elegantly simple mouse only controls, Ghoul Smash lets you experience the sheer exhilaration of obliterating foes to dust, all while reveling in a flood of dopamine-fueled rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ghoul Smash offers a hardcore mode as well for those that wish to try the ultimate challenge, and will feature six classes with passive bonuses on full release.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435910/extras/fa12b6632a0a6c2c7dd4c146c8dcae8f.poster.avif?t=1727827290\" width=618 height=78 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435910/extras/fa12b6632a0a6c2c7dd4c146c8dcae8f.webm?t=1727827290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435910/extras/fa12b6632a0a6c2c7dd4c146c8dcae8f.mp4?t=1727827290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Unique Physics Based Combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    2 Acts with 20 Stages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Scaling Endgame</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Hardcore Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Over 300 different items and equipment!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    ARPG Style Loot</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    50+ Skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Skillpoints and Leveling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Crafting, Shopping, and Forging</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Multiple Enemy-types and Bosses!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Easter Eggs and Secrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Easy to Learn</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your character can be molded into the playstyle of your choice. Whether you want to bash targets with melee or hit from afar with magic or ranged, your equipment will drastically change how you interact with enemies. Each piece of armor comes with it's own stats and art so you can mix and match what suits you best!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435910/extras/df5b6ac462cf3427bc7569bfd10cdd91.poster.avif?t=1727827290\" width=618 height=78 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435910/extras/df5b6ac462cf3427bc7569bfd10cdd91.webm?t=1727827290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435910/extras/df5b6ac462cf3427bc7569bfd10cdd91.mp4?t=1727827290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You can join the Ghoul Smash discord by clicking the link on the sidebar to get the latest news about Ghoul Smash and participate in discussion about the game with the developer!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435910/extras/c27cb8932069f3c01a62b5ca12e194fb.poster.avif?t=1727827290\" width=618 height=78 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435910/extras/c27cb8932069f3c01a62b5ca12e194fb.webm?t=1727827290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435910/extras/c27cb8932069f3c01a62b5ca12e194fb.mp4?t=1727827290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Imagine if pool was transformed into an ARPG - that's Ghoul Smash! This turn-based physics game invites you to smash into enemies, face off against formidable bosses, and claim epic loot, craft gear, and invest into classes. With its elegantly simple mouse only controls, Ghoul Smash lets you experience the sheer exhilaration of obliterating foes to dust, all while reveling in a flood of dopamine-fueled rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ghoul Smash offers a hardcore mode as well for those that wish to try the ultimate challenge, and will feature six classes with passive bonuses on full release.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435910/extras/fa12b6632a0a6c2c7dd4c146c8dcae8f.poster.avif?t=1727827290\" width=618 height=78 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435910/extras/fa12b6632a0a6c2c7dd4c146c8dcae8f.webm?t=1727827290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435910/extras/fa12b6632a0a6c2c7dd4c146c8dcae8f.mp4?t=1727827290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Unique Physics Based Combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    2 Acts with 20 Stages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Scaling Endgame</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Hardcore Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Over 300 different items and equipment!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    ARPG Style Loot</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    50+ Skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Skillpoints and Leveling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Crafting, Shopping, and Forging</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Multiple Enemy-types and Bosses!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Easter Eggs and Secrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Easy to Learn</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your character can be molded into the playstyle of your choice. Whether you want to bash targets with melee or hit from afar with magic or ranged, your equipment will drastically change how you interact with enemies. Each piece of armor comes with it's own stats and art so you can mix and match what suits you best!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435910/extras/df5b6ac462cf3427bc7569bfd10cdd91.poster.avif?t=1727827290\" width=618 height=78 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435910/extras/df5b6ac462cf3427bc7569bfd10cdd91.webm?t=1727827290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435910/extras/df5b6ac462cf3427bc7569bfd10cdd91.mp4?t=1727827290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You can join the Ghoul Smash discord by clicking the link on the sidebar to get the latest news about Ghoul Smash and participate in discussion about the game with the developer!</p>",
